{"tid":2463801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新疆棉風暴】不向中國屈膝！德品牌Hugo Boss改聲明稱不容忍強制勞動","createTime":"2021-03-27T03:51:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-27T04:33:04.000Z","uid":13663,"like":24,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"d2b52488b45200ceafc02aa77bad47d942d9c807","tid":2463801,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T03:51:41.000Z","msg":"瑞典服裝品牌H&amp;M與美國運動用品大廠Nike去年因關切新疆人權問題，而發表不採用新疆棉花的聲明，沒想到卻在1年後的近日突然被中國官方重提，並藉此發動民間抵制行動。同樣受到波及的德國品牌Hugo Boss一度發中文聲明稱會繼續購買新疆棉花，但今早突然改稱，絕不忍受強制勞動，目前也沒有採購來自新疆的原料。"},{"pid":"f5461f0509a14b58f1e63675a196db4a4e2d8e92","tid":2463801,"uid":13663,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T03:52:27.000Z","msg":"Hugo Boss前晚（3/25)一度在官方微博表態支持新疆棉，發聲明表示將「繼續採購和支持新疆棉花」，迅速得到中國媒體和網友讚賞，相關微博下方，幾乎都是「支持新疆棉花」、「支持尊重中國的企業」的評論。然而Hugo Boss的中文官方微博今早卻刪除該發文，並附上英文版官方聲明連結。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">Hugo Boss在英文聲明中強調，該公司管理政策採取嚴格道德標準，並尊重人權，更不容忍強制勞動。該公司表示，目前沒有採購來自新疆地區的原料，會仔細檢查所有供應商是否符合相關的價值觀和標準，並強調珍惜與中國合作夥伴的友誼。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n德國之聲稍早報導，Hugo Boss在此議題似乎採取兩套標準，微博上的發文和發給德國之聲的德語聲明內容截然不同。在德語版的聲明也強調，「致力於尊重人權，承認聯合國《世界人權宣言》的基本價值觀和國際勞工組織的核心公約，絕不容忍任何形式的強制、強迫勞動」、「迄今為止，Hugo Boss尚未直接從新疆地區購買任何產品」。<br />\n<br />\n報導同時指出，有關美歐各國因新疆人權問題制裁中國，以及外國品牌因強制勞動而拒用新疆棉花等議題，中國網友其實了解極少。主要是因為中國媒體並未報導整件事情的來龍去脈，並故意引導中國人民以為，整件事是因為美國人想保護自己國家種植棉花的農民。另有網友以為，這是歐盟想操控棉花的價格，或和中國打貿易戰的談判籌碼。"},{"pid":"cc5872ca61dc589e736cc61ac0f729ba342274ee","tid":2463801,"uid":13663,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T03:52:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210327/M4OSTSFVKRFEFCDATHJC5EYXSY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210327%2FM4OSTSFVKRFEFCDATHJC5EYXSY%2F&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWgWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=d7942fc3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210327%2FM4OSTSFVKRFEFCDATHJC5EYXSY%2F&h=2871c981\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210327/M4OSTSFVKRFEFCDATHJC5EYXSY/</a>"},{"pid":"950acbc6a58faa80b659b5918d2b93c9a742935f","tid":2463801,"uid":11148,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T03:54:29.000Z","msg":"支那啲分公司做得幾好，逼啲總公司表態選邊站<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多公司本身諗住唔出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ef7240ed69ff9bebfef006e54bb7474f5973170","tid":2463801,"uid":138868,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T03:54:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-cdn.9gag.com/photo/ag02Qyw_700b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-cdn.9gag.com%2Fphoto%2Fag02Qyw_700b.jpg&h=4cdcf21d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9c8774adecfd31bf40f03323f7aa9a0b6cba1af6","tid":2463801,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T03:55:12.000Z","msg":"德國車廠唔會咁諗<br />\n<br />\n中國市場實在太大<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net/media/image/2020/09/24251f45e0d44594a123c9a2481ccdc5.png?imageView2/1/w/1080/h/900/format/jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd32kak7w9u5ewj.cloudfront.net%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2020%2F09%2F24251f45e0d44594a123c9a2481ccdc5.png%3FimageView2%2F1%2Fw%2F1080%2Fh%2F900%2Fformat%2Fjpg&h=7199f13a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.businessfocus.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/v-525_.jpg?auto=format&amp;w=830&amp;q=100\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.businessfocus.io%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2Fv-525_.jpg%3Fauto%3Dformat%26w%3D830%26q%3D100&h=fdca33e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"50d4088234c3665e5aeb3a23ae703828bd7536b8","tid":2463801,"uid":55089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T03:55:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/